, 
<figureCitation id="B2FC2A4E196029437741FA1CFC86FA12" box="[787,836,1501,1525]" captionStart="Figure 15" captionStartId="31.[144,211,1560,1582]" captionTargetBox="[144,1104,168,1528]" captionTargetId="figure@31.[144,1104,168,1528]" captionTargetPageId="31" captionText="Figure 15. Distribution records of Megalopta species. (A) M. chaperi Vachal; (B) M. guimaraesi Santos &amp; Silveira (black circles) and M. mura sp. n. (grey squares); (C) M. piraha sp. n (grey squares) and M. yanomami sp. n. (black circles); (D) M. atlantica Santos &amp; Silveira (grey square), M. guarani sp. n (triangle), M. xavante sp. n (hexagon), M. karitiana sp. n (black circle), M. mapinguari sp. n (black square) and M. purpurata Smith (grey circle)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4004489" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4004489/files/figure.png" pageId="48" pageNumber="623">15D</figureCitation>
